12
00:00:32,906 --> 00:00:35,510
<i>e de qualquer um
que queira prejudicá-la.</i>

13
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:39,081
<i>Eu sou... a Supergirl!</i>

14
00:00:40,390 --> 00:00:41,935
